WEBVTT


00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.280
Zhong Yak Yong was a sillhawk scholar, politician,

00:00:04.281 --> 00:00:08.341
poet and inventor of the late Joseon Dynasty

00:00:08.440 --> 00:00:11.580
who presented innovative ideas in various fields,

00:00:11.840 --> 00:00:16.140
and his ideas and techniques still have a great influence today.

00:00:16.480 --> 00:00:18.320
His most innovative contribution

00:00:18.321 --> 00:00:22.021
may be his critical ideas about political and social systems.

00:00:22.400 --> 00:00:26.160
Zhang advocated for improving the quality of life of the people

00:00:26.161 --> 00:00:29.821
and reforming the political system based on social fairness.

00:00:30.200 --> 00:00:32.080
His work, Mockman Seamsell,

00:00:32.081 --> 00:00:36.201
contained his deep insight into how rulers should govern their people,

00:00:36.202 --> 00:00:39.041
which contained universal values that could be applied

00:00:39.042 --> 00:00:42.661
not only to Joseon but also to modern society.

00:00:42.840 --> 00:00:45.920
In addition, it contributed to the development of IQ

00:00:45.921 --> 00:00:50.121
thiology in Joseon by systematically classifying and recording

00:00:50.122 --> 00:00:53.661
Joseon's fishery resources through Jasun Aoba.
